# Metrics & Business Case Rules

## Objective
데이터 기반 비즈니스 케이스 구축 및 성공 메트릭 정의

## Required Inputs
- tam_analysis: TAM/SAM/SOM 분석 결과
- solution_definition: 정의된 솔루션과 기능
- competitor_pricing: 경쟁사 가격 정보
- development_costs: 예상 개발 비용

## Process Steps

### 1. Financial Modeling Research
Use Perplexity MCP for (설정되지 않은 경우 Tavily MCP 사용):
- Query: "[industry] SaaS metrics benchmarks CAC LTV"
- Query: "[market] pricing models strategies"
- Query: "[industry] unit economics benchmarks"
- Query: "startup financial projections [market] examples"
- Query: "[industry] customer acquisition costs channels"

### 2. Metrics Definition
Define metrics across:
- Business metrics (revenue, costs, margins)
- Product metrics (adoption, engagement, retention)
- Customer metrics (NPS, CSAT, churn)
- Operational metrics (efficiency, quality)

### 3. Financial Projections
Create projections for:
- Revenue forecast (3-5 years)
- Cost structure analysis
- Break-even analysis
- ROI calculation
- Sensitivity analysis

